<li><a href="http://www.law.cornell.edu/anncon/html/amdt16toc_user.html" class="external text" title="http://www.law.cornell.edu/anncon/html/amdt16toc_user.html" rel="nofollow">CRS Annotated Constitution: Sixteenth Amendment</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.law.emory.edu/FEDERAL/usconst/amend.html" class="external text" title="http://www.law.emory.edu/FEDERAL/usconst/amend.html" rel="nofollow">Emory University School of Law website lists proposal and ratification details for amendments to the United States Constitution</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.law.cornell.edu/supct/html/historics/USSC_CR_0157_0429_ZO.html" class="external text" title="http://www.law.cornell.edu/supct/html/historics/USSC_CR_0157_0429_ZO.html" rel="nofollow">Pollock Decision</a> The decision overruled by the Sixteenth Amendment</li>
<li><a href="http://caselaw.lp.findlaw.com/scripts/getcase.pl?navby=search&amp;court=US&amp;case=/us/240/1.html" class="external text" title="http://caselaw.lp.findlaw.com/scripts/getcase.pl?navby=search&amp;court=US&amp;case=/us/240/1.html" rel="nofollow">Brushaber Decision</a> Supreme Court opinion on the apportionment clause of the Constitution.</li>
<li><a href="http://caselaw.lp.findlaw.com/scripts/getcase.pl?court=US&amp;vol=240&amp;invol=103" class="external text" title="http://caselaw.lp.findlaw.com/scripts/getcase.pl?court=US&amp;vol=240&amp;invol=103" rel="nofollow">Stanton Decision</a> - no new power of taxation (affirming constitutionality of income tax after Sixteenth Amendment)</li>
</ul>
